Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過分和平 簡直都要打哈欠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來見你了哦 黑虎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一次 我一定要將你…
